Package com.dua3.meja.model

Interface SheetEvent

All Superinterfaces:
Event<Sheet>
All Known Implementing Classes:
SheetEvent.ActiveCellChanged, SheetEvent.CellChanged, SheetEvent.CellStyleChanged, SheetEvent.CellValueChanged, SheetEvent.ColumnsAdded, SheetEvent.LayoutChanged, SheetEvent.RowsAdded, SheetEvent.SplitChanged, SheetEvent.ZoomChanged
public interface SheetEvent extends Event<Sheet>
SheetEvent is an interface that extends the Event class for handling various events related to a Sheet object.
